cess=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104opw1665702710725.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/opw1665702710725.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/opw1665702710725.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"opw1665702710725\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      First Occurrence Identifier </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">ASCII string that marks the beginning of the first occurrence of an included entity. </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"opw1665702710725__section_t5h_sqg_pwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d837245e51\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"opw1665702710725__p_d7271e1_d7272e1_d7273e1\">Use this definition only if the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Identification\n               Type</span> species that a string identifier will be used, either alone or in\n            combination with a binary length.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"opw1665702710725__section_vsr_5qg_pwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d837245e63\">Applies to</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"opw1665702710725__ul_zlh_vqg_pwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"opw1665702710725__li_d39734e1_d39735e1_d39736e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"hzd1665702710226.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hzd1665702710226.html\" title=\"A Modeled Entity Interface is a Development Object that defines a reusable value for the Database Interface property of a Database Entity.\">Modeled Entity Interface</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xbb1665702769022.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Data Storage</a><p>Field interface definitions, as defined in the Database Interface property, determine how data is stored in a specific DBMS storage format, and how Uniface deals with the data when it is retrieved. The definitions specify the Uniface data type and packing code, which are mapped by the DBMS connector to the DBMS data type, known as a storage format.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3615044\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3615044\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "First Occurrence Identifier Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated März 01, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 First Occurrence Identifier ASCII string that marks the beginning of the first occurrence of an included entity. Description Use this definition only if the Identification Type species that a string identifier will be used, either alone or in combination with a binary length. Applies to Modeled Entity Interface Related Links Data Storage Field interface definitions, as defined in the Database Interface property, determine how data is stored in a specific DBMS storage format, and how Uniface deals with the data when it is retrieved. The definitions specify the Uniface data type and packing code, which are mapped by the DBMS connector to the DBMS data type, known as a storage format. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}